<%- include('partials/header') %>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Know Before You Go</h2>
    <p class="lead">A few helpful notes to make your day on the water smooth and memorable.</p>

    <div class="card">
      <ul>
        <li>Fishing license: All anglers 16+ need a valid state license. <a href="<%= settings.licenseUrl %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener">State license page</a>.</li>
        <li>What's included: Rods, reels, tackle, bait, safety gear, and guided instruction.</li>
        <li>What to bring: Weather-appropriate layers, polarized sunglasses, snacks, and a reusable water bottle.</li>
        <li>Weather plans: Trips run rain or shine unless conditions are unsafe.</li>
        <li>Fish cleaning: We can guide you to local cleaning stations and rules.</li>
        <li>Arrival: Plan to arrive 15 minutes early for a quick safety brief.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
